title: Creatures 3
description:
Good game, got hard to find for a while. Full CD image and as such it has all the files needed. Just use Daemon to mount it and you&#039;re good to go.

Somewhat of a niche game, it&#039;s sort of like a more advanced, 2d Sims set in space.

Enjoy and share!

[Also, my connection isn&#039;t ideal for uploading so sadly you may be in for a wait, and it probably won&#039;t kick in for 40 minutes after I upload.]
